{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-classic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-301-to-400/problem-374-maximum-integer-partition-product","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"block":"project-euler-problems-301-to-400","demoType":null,"title":"Vežba 374: Najveći stepen množenja delova celog broja","description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>Raspored celog broja $n$ je način predstavljanja $n$ kao zbir pozitivnih celih brojeva.</p>\n<p>Particija koja se razlikuje samo po redosledu svojih delova smatra se jednakom. Particija $n$ na različite delove je particija $n$ gde svaki deo nastupa samo jednom.</p>\n<p>Deljenje 5 na različite delove je:</p>\n<p>5, 4 + 1 na 3 + 2.</p>\n<p>Neka je $f(n)$ najveći multiplikativni merač bilo kog delilatelja $n$ na različite delove, a neka je $m(n)$ broj komponenti bilo kog delilatelja $n$ koji imaju taj multiplikativni merač.</p>\n<p>Dakle, $f(5) = 6$ i $m(5) = 2$.</p>\n<p>Za $n = 10$, rasporedak sa najvećim proizvodom je $10 = 2 + 3 + 5$, koji daje $f(10) = 30$ i $m(10) = 3$. Njihov proizvod je, $f(10) \\times m(10) = 30 \\times 3 = 90$</p>\n<p>Može se dokazati da $\\sum f(n) \\times m(n)$ kwa $1 ≤ n ≤ 100 = 1\\,683\\,550\\,844\\,462$.</p>\n<p>Izračunaj $\\sum f(n) \\times m(n)$ za $1 ≤ n ≤ {10}^{14}$. Izračunaj rezultat modulo $982\\,451\\,653$, sa bazom od miliona 50.</p>\n</section>","id":"5900f4e51000cf542c50fff6","hasEditableBoundaries":false,"instructions":"","notes":null,"challengeType":1,"helpCategory":"Euler","videoUrl":null,"superBlock":"project-euler","translationPending":false,"forumTopicId":302036,"hooks":null,"fields":{"slug":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-301-to-400/problem-374-maximum-integer-partition-product"},"required":[],"usesMultifileEditor":false,"challengeFiles":[{"fileKey":"scriptjs","ext":"js","name":"script","contents":"function maximumIntegerPartitionProduct() {\n\n  return true;\n}\n\nmaximumIntegerPartitionProduct();","head":null,"tail":null,"editableRegionBoundaries":[],"history":["script.js"]}],"saveSubmissionToDB":null,"tests":[{"text":"<p><code>maximumIntegerPartitionProduct()</code> treba vratiti <code>334420941</code>.</p>","testString":"assert.strictEqual(maximumIntegerPartitionProduct(), 334420941);"}]}}},"pageContext":{"challengeMeta":{"blockHashSlug":"/learn/project-euler/#project-euler-problems-301-to-400","dashedName":"problem-374-maximum-integer-partition-product","certification":"project-euler","disableLoopProtectTests":true,"disableLoopProtectPreview":false,"superBlock":"project-euler","chapter":null,"module":null,"block":"project-euler-problems-301-to-400","isFirstStep":false,"template":null,"required":[],"isLastChallengeInBlock":false,"nextChallengePath":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-301-to-400/problem-375-minimum-of-subsequences","prevChallengePath":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-301-to-400/problem-373-circumscribed-circles","id":"5900f4e51000cf542c50fff6","saveSubmissionToDB":null},"projectPreview":{"challengeData":{"challengeType":1,"challengeFiles":[{"name":"script","ext":"js","contents":"// solution required","history":["script.js"],"fileKey":"scriptjs"}]}},"id":"/learn/project-euler/project-euler-problems-301-to-400/problem-374-maximum-integer-partition-product"}},"staticQueryHashes":["3858520367"],"slicesMap":{}}